<a target="_new" href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=70593">Feran Hide Drum</a>
<br />

<br />
Reportedly, collect four <a target="_new" href="http://lucy.allakhazam.com/item.html?id=77645">Icy Crystal</a>s, which drop from ferans in Wall of Slaughter and Riftseeker's Sanctum, and turn them in to the four portals in the wall near the Girplan Guardian.  This will spawn <a target="_new" href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=16676">Tarn Icewind</a>, who is doable by 1-2 well geared groups (ie Time+ gear).
<br />

<br />
Among runes and various other loot (i've heard i dunno), he drops this drum rarely.  Good luck.</span></td>
