				<td colspan="2"><span>I have got this drum from the Icewind portal event. 210 dmg is what i do with this drum and IM3 (yea i am slacker and will get IM4 some day).
<br />

<br />
Anyway sure it can be mquest with multi people turning in crystals from what i understand 1 crystal to each portal must all be turn in within a certain amount of time after each other.
<br />
You have like a 5min break after turn ins (or at least we did) before the fun starts.
<br />

<br />
Not that hard of an event. Keep ur tank on tarn icewind while having part of ur raid during the entire fight killing adds (2 every 1-3 mins spawn set time i just forgot to watch it although we could keep them down np at all before next adds). Those not killing adds need to first kill the 4 crystals on the sides of the room (ones u did turn into). Once those are destoried you can now send the crystal group to kill icewind (who before crystals are killed will regen faster then u can do dmg). He does have an ae CR not hard to resist does around 800dmg and atk debuff for about 1-2min or so.
<br />

<br />
For us he droped the drum (which i won), greater rune, and glowing rune.</span></td>
